{"tid":1900044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老實講，如果上年6月9號知道而家發生咩事，會唔會放棄？","createTime":"2020-02-27T03:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T06:21:35.000Z","uid":229095,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"da1c81d6f2c0cdc1325ebf9866d86b10ca8a9c92","tid":1900044,"uid":229095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:50:50.000Z","msg":"7000幾個田足比人拉左<br />\n冇左咁多野<br />\n到頭來好似咩都得唔到<br />\n而家個社會又開始似變返2014咁大愛和平左膠<br />\n泛民就開始變返和平抗爭<br />\n仲有一班人仲希望光復左香港之後可以救返義士同埋拎返失去左嘅野<br />\n其實你同我都知冇咩可能<br />\n唔好再係到講話咩要煲底見黑驚死全家<br />\n係冇意思<br />\n<br />\n如果比我返返69<br />\n我寧願做順民做豬算鳩數"},{"pid":"5cef6269a9541ca6b5077d4270bcde6ac6d78048","tid":1900044,"uid":229095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:51:17.000Z","msg":"打錯字<br />\n係手足"},{"pid":"2af7109aa496bde62ebd9ebaa06d930dc42c9ba9","tid":1900044,"uid":156130,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:52:52.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n抗爭從來唔係一朝一夕嘅事<br />\n可唔可以話有黃花崗之役就要放棄革命？<br />\n<br />\n日後嘅抗爭就係今日我地所做嘅一切去影響後世<br />\n<br />\n唔好放棄呀手足"},{"pid":"8fc73e4af7d474e3e849a9f5c5e8df9665b5f62d","tid":1900044,"uid":138197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:53:05.000Z","msg":"我會放棄 唔想有手足受傷"},{"pid":"372aec85e38a960bbf342bed658aac5cccd88026","tid":1900044,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fc73e4af7d474e3e849a9f5c5e8df9665b5f62d","tid":1900044,"uid":138197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:53:05.000Z","msg":"我會放棄 唔想有手足受傷"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"唔發生呢班人都係飲飲食食唔會變你手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b14f155992b833be09afb78fe81f447ddd0d5cc","tid":1900044,"uid":138197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"372aec85e38a960bbf342bed658aac5cccd88026","tid":1900044,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fc73e4af7d474e3e849a9f5c5e8df9665b5f62d","tid":1900044,"uid":138197,"li